		<RichText x="66" y="704" width="505" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">拥有<span color="#ffdfbf">200</span><span>点计量上限。角色</span><span color="#ffdfbf">进入或维持</span><span>「夜魂加持」状态时，其均会积攒</span><span color="#bfffbf">15</span><span>计量；当充满时，构型械就会立即中断其他技能，并开始球状雷弹的准备。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>计量规则更改：每秒积攒</span><span color="#bfffbf">2</span><span>计量，角色</span><span color="#ffdfbf">进入</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">维持</span><span>「夜魂加持」状态时，将积攒</span><span color="#bfffbf">5</span><span>/</span><span color="#bfffbf">3</span><span>计量。计量充满后，本机制将不再重复出现。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
