		</Rect>
		<RichText x="67" y="960" width="138" height="26" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffbfbf">(N5) <span color="#ffffff">雷贯屏障：</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="992" width="507" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">开局立即展开，厚度为<span color="#ffbfbf">200%生命值</span><span>，</span><span textDecoration="underline">应战对策</span><span>充满后被破坏。击破后将对构型械造成一次真伤，其值为屏障展开期间</span><span color="#ffdfbf">50%所受伤害</span><span>，不超过</span><span color="#ffdfbf">50%构型械生命值</span><span>。首次瘫痪后将不再形成该屏障及抗性提升效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="67" y="832" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="166" height="26" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">固态燃素与汲聚械：</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="864" width="496" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仅「回声之子」成员可直接攀爬，高度接近岩脊，其余角色可卡模型逃课。进入其上方的屏障内可直接击破「汲聚械」，击破所有汲聚械可使构型械瘫痪15s，并扣除其<span color="#ffccbf">15%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1538" y="320" width="441" height="65" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">构型械驻于原地，于自身炮筒发射3枚雷轰弹，落地爆炸，每枚造成<span color="#ffacff">70%</span><span>伤害，并留下雷地面，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">7%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/栗烈之役-秘源机兵构型械%B7裂解剪钳.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1520" y="233">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/栗烈之役-秘源机兵构型械%B7裂解剪钳.assets/Image_23.png')" x="1376" y="246" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/栗烈之役-秘源机兵构型械%B7裂解剪钳.assets/Image_24.png')" x="1396" y="267" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1538" y="512" width="444" height="65" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">过于靠近构型械时，构型械化作巨星爪掌并拍下，造成<span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害，同时产生6道纵方向中心合拢的激光，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，聚拢后发生爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/栗烈之役-秘源机兵构型械%B7裂解剪钳.assets/Image_25.png')" x="1519" y="426">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/栗烈之役-秘源机兵构型械%B7裂解剪钳.assets/Image_26.png')" x="1396" y="459" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/栗烈之役-秘源机兵构型械%B7裂解剪钳.assets/Image_27.png')" x="1376" y="438" blendMode="normal">
